==Trivia==
*The Sire, as well as its [[respiratory system]]s, have multiple examine options that can be seen throughout the fight.
*It is one of the few monsters that does not have a defensive animation; rather, it loops its idle animation instead.
*Despite being a solo-only boss, the Sire's area-of-effect attack at 33% health and poison fumes can harm other players if they are in range.
*The sire cannot be defeated before its explosion attack. If the player manages to kill it before then it will respawn  where the fight left off with about 1/3 of its max health

